name: natural-communities
notes: This dataset shows the locations of known tracts of high quality natural communities in Kansas, generalized to the PLSS section. It is not a compehensive dataset of all such areas in Kansas, as most of the state has not been surveyed for the presence of natural communities, but shows the status of the database as it currently exists.
